Stockton.Country Club, California:
Country Club is a census-designated place (CDP) in San Joaquin County, California, United States. The population was 9,379 at the 2010 census, down from 9,462 at the 2000 census.


== Geography ==
According to the United States Census Bureau, the CDP has a total area of 2.0 square miles (5.2 km2), of which, 1.8 square miles (4.7 km2) of it is land and 0.2 square miles (0.52 km2) of it (7.63%) is water.
